  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393170/extras/cb62220e55bd511b0114c1a9ca8dee99.avif?t=1770607560\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Description:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Whispers Left at Night</i> is a exploration-based indie game that tells the story of the protagonist, Yunika, and their experiences in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the title may sound poetic, it’s actually a house-cleaning game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging character interactions, including dialogue filled with humorous meme references.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxed exploration with the ability to collect furniture inside the house.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the hidden truth behind the story as you delve deeper into the game!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Note:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The English version of this game was translated using ChatGPT. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some translation inaccuracies may be present. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please consider this before purchasing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your understanding and support.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393170/extras/cb62220e55bd511b0114c1a9ca8dee99.avif?t=1770607560\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Description:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Whispers Left at Night</i> is a exploration-based indie game that tells the story of the protagonist, Yunika, and their experiences in the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While the title may sound poetic, it’s actually a house-cleaning game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging character interactions, including dialogue filled with humorous meme references.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxed exploration with the ability to collect furniture inside the house.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the hidden truth behind the story as you delve deeper into the game!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Note:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The English version of this game was translated using ChatGPT. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some translation inaccuracies may be present. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please consider this before purchasing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for your understanding and support.</p>",
